Description: Enterprise video conferencing for conference rooms
 Croom transforms any Linux device into an enterprise-grade
 video conferencing appliance with support for Google Meet,
 Microsoft Teams, Zoom, and Webex. Features include:
  - Multi-platform meeting support
  - Edge AI for auto-framing and noise reduction
  - Touch screen room management UI
  - Central fleet management dashboard
  - Zero-touch device provisioning
